data.description: Beautiful and Tropically inspired home in the beautiful Barefoot Bay.  This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and an additional room that can be used as an additional bedroom or whatever your imagination desires.  A beautiful enclosed patio also offers additional space, in addition to a big kitchen, large family and living rooms, and a perfectly located lot.  This FHA / VA home has approved Engineering plans, along with a 2020 Roof, 2023 A/C, 2020 Water Heater, and so much more.  This resort community comes with 3 heated pools, golf course, shopping, pier, tennis and much more.    This is a rare find and an amazing property.
